<p>
  There's a Vietnamese saying — "mưu sự tại nhân, thành sự tại
  thiên." We plan, but heaven decides. Doesn't mean we stop
  planning though. It means we plan harder, and hold the results
  loosely.
</p>
<p>
  90-day cut plan is on track. The OMSCS apps are submitted. The
  code keeps shipping. Now we wait, and we keep grinding.
</p>
